WEBVTT

00:00:00.033 --> 00:00:04.234
Easter Puja. Istanbul - Turkey 22 April 2001.

00:00:04.767 --> 00:00:08.767
Today we have gathered here

00:00:10.300 --> 00:00:14.300
to do the puja of Easter.

00:00:16.234 --> 00:00:20.501
In the history of spirituality,

00:00:20.601 --> 00:00:23.501
it is one of the greatest days

00:00:23.567 --> 00:00:30.100
when we find Christ rose from the dead.

00:00:32.701 --> 00:00:35.667
It is very significant and symbolic

00:00:36.300 --> 00:00:39.234
that in Sahaja Yoga, also

00:00:39.801 --> 00:00:41.701
what we have done,

00:00:42.367 --> 00:00:48.234
is to rise from the dead – into life.

00:00:49.234 --> 00:00:51.467
It is to be understood

00:00:51.567 --> 00:00:56.434
that resurrection is the message for all of us,

00:00:56.534 --> 00:00:58.667
for the whole world.

00:00:58.767 --> 00:01:01.734
We have to resurrect ourselves.

00:01:01.801 --> 00:01:09.667
There was no need for Jesus to do that.

00:01:09.734 --> 00:01:13.767
But He was a model, model of a saint,

00:01:14.033 --> 00:01:16.734
model of a realised soul,

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:21.133
model of a person who came all the way

00:01:21.234 --> 00:01:24.501
from the heavens to save us.

00:01:24.567 --> 00:01:26.601
So this resurrection is also

00:01:26.701 --> 00:01:30.334
part and parcel of our lives.

00:01:31.567 --> 00:01:35.567
It is so symbolic, so very symbolic,

00:01:36.767 --> 00:01:38.801
that we were,

00:01:41.534 --> 00:01:45.634
in our consciousness, lost people.

00:01:46.467 --> 00:01:49.467
We had no control over ourselves

00:01:49.534 --> 00:01:53.167
as to know the way our mind told us to go.

00:01:53.234 --> 00:01:56.234
We had no balance with the mind

00:01:56.334 --> 00:01:58.334
and our physical being,

00:01:59.167 --> 00:02:02.100
no balance of any kind in life

00:02:02.167 --> 00:02:04.467
and used to go at random,

00:02:04.567 --> 00:02:08.000
whichever way we thought was good.

00:02:08.100 --> 00:02:10.634
There was no wisdom about it.

00:02:10.701 --> 00:02:17.334
As it is, Jesus was the incarnation of Shri Ganesha.

00:02:19.100 --> 00:02:22.100
It’s a very difficult task He has performed.

00:02:22.534 --> 00:02:24.501
He used to convince people

00:02:24.601 --> 00:02:29.234
who were absolutely ignorant about spirituality,

00:02:29.334 --> 00:02:33.501
who just knew about money and nothing else.

00:02:33.601 --> 00:02:36.067
He came in those days

00:02:36.133 --> 00:02:41.534
when people had no idea about spirituality at all, at all.

00:02:42.133 --> 00:02:45.067
But, somehow,

00:02:45.133 --> 00:02:47.133
it all worked out

00:02:48.067 --> 00:02:50.501
in such a beautiful manner

00:02:50.567 --> 00:02:54.133
that people have started understanding

00:02:54.200 --> 00:02:59.234
that He communicated that resurrection is the important point.

00:03:01.667 --> 00:03:04.701
He knew when the resurrection takes place,

00:03:04.767 --> 00:03:07.133
the Kundalini rises

00:03:07.234 --> 00:03:12.033
and connects you to the Divine Power, which is all-pervading.

00:03:12.100 --> 00:03:14.133
Then you start understanding

00:03:14.200 --> 00:03:16.634
that there’s a life beyond

00:03:16.701 --> 00:03:19.267
the life that you have made.

00:03:19.367 --> 00:03:21.367
There’s another type of life,

00:03:22.067 --> 00:03:27.234
a higher type of life, which connects you to the Divine Power.

00:03:28.234 --> 00:03:33.234
And then this Divine Power gives you the Absolute Truth.

00:03:34.367 --> 00:03:37.167
If you grow more and more,

00:03:37.234 --> 00:03:40.100
you will know Absolute Truth

00:03:40.200 --> 00:03:42.133
because so far you don’t know.

00:03:42.200 --> 00:03:44.400
So we have been doing wrong things,

00:03:44.467 --> 00:03:47.601
going in the wrong way, getting lost.

00:03:47.701 --> 00:03:51.534
Also we were listening to people who were just boasting

00:03:51.601 --> 00:03:55.133
and were saying they know about the Truth.

00:03:55.200 --> 00:03:58.033
But when you yourself discover the Truth,

00:03:58.100 --> 00:04:00.467
you are a different person.

00:04:00.567 --> 00:04:05.634
You discovery is so innate and so real

00:04:05.734 --> 00:04:09.033
that you discard all that is unreal.

00:04:09.133 --> 00:04:11.367
Very easily you can discard it

00:04:11.434 --> 00:04:16.167
and you don’t find it difficult to get rid of it.

00:04:16.234 --> 00:04:21.467
In this conference, as you know, we have more of Muslim people,

00:04:21.567 --> 00:04:27.133
Islamic people, who have been so much misguided all over the world.

00:04:27.200 --> 00:04:30.434
They have been told all kinds of stories

00:04:30.501 --> 00:04:34.167
and hatred among people or others.

00:04:34.234 --> 00:04:37.067
This Islamic bhoots

00:04:37.133 --> 00:04:39.267
is going from bad to worse

00:04:39.367 --> 00:04:42.234
and people want to believe in it.

00:04:42.334 --> 00:04:46.634
Especially in my country there’s a very, very big problem

00:04:46.701 --> 00:04:49.767
with this Islamic influence

00:04:50.000 --> 00:04:53.067
because they are nowhere near Islam,

00:04:53.133 --> 00:04:56.267
they have nothing to do with Mohammed-sahib,

00:04:56.334 --> 00:04:58.601
but they are thinking

00:04:58.667 --> 00:05:02.067
that they are correct and what they are doing is correct.

00:05:02.133 --> 00:05:06.501
They’re trying to spread Muslim religion.

00:05:06.601 --> 00:05:10.400
What’s the use? What’s the purpose? I can’t understand.

00:05:10.467 --> 00:05:13.501
Unless and until you get your realisation,

00:05:13.567 --> 00:05:17.133
you are a useless human being, good for nothing.

00:05:17.200 --> 00:05:20.167
You can hate others, you can beat others,

00:05:20.234 --> 00:05:24.701
you can kill others and it’s going on all over the place.

00:05:24.767 --> 00:05:28.634
Surprising thing that all this nonsense is going on

00:05:28.701 --> 00:05:32.634
everywhere in the world in the name of Mohammed-sahib.

00:05:32.734 --> 00:05:37.367
So in one shot, one side you put Christ

00:05:37.434 --> 00:05:39.534
for another crucifixion,

00:05:39.601 --> 00:05:43.133
on the other side Mohammed-sahib for his crucifixion.

00:05:43.200 --> 00:05:45.067
They cannot fight, you see.

00:05:45.133 --> 00:05:51.067
They’re on the same line. They’re on the same understanding.

00:05:51.133 --> 00:05:53.067
How can they fight? But

00:05:53.133 --> 00:05:56.100
their disciples are fighting so badly all over

00:05:56.200 --> 00:05:59.067
that sometimes it really breaks you,

00:05:59.133 --> 00:06:04.634
when you only hear about how people are fighting for nonsense.

00:06:09.567 --> 00:06:14.501
In His life, Christ did not marry.

00:06:15.367 --> 00:06:20.100
He did not and He never needed also.

00:06:20.200 --> 00:06:22.133
He did not marry.

00:06:22.200 --> 00:06:26.200
And at a very young age He was crucified.

00:06:26.734 --> 00:06:31.334
That crucifixion shows that He was not afraid of death

00:06:32.133 --> 00:06:35.033
and He knew that He would resurrect Himself.

00:06:35.100 --> 00:06:38.701
This He had to do through the Agnya Chakra.

00:06:38.767 --> 00:06:42.000
Agnya Chakra is, as you know, is very constricted.

00:06:42.067 --> 00:06:45.100
And through that constriction He had to go through,

00:06:45.167 --> 00:06:48.400
for which He had to get killed.

00:06:48.501 --> 00:06:52.501
And He accepted that. He accepted

00:06:54.133 --> 00:06:59.467
with full heart that that’s the ordeal He has to go through.

00:06:59.567 --> 00:07:02.267
In the same way, your Sahasrara

00:07:02.334 --> 00:07:05.067
can be only achieved through the Agnya

00:07:05.133 --> 00:07:07.801
and the Agnya has to be opened out.

00:07:08.067 --> 00:07:12.100
But for that, you don’t have to get hanged,

00:07:12.200 --> 00:07:15.100
you don’t have to be crucified,

00:07:15.200 --> 00:07:19.067
but you have to crucify your ego.

00:07:19.133 --> 00:07:21.667
The first point is ego.

00:07:21.767 --> 00:07:26.067
You have such ego that you cannot get rid of it.

00:07:26.567 --> 00:07:30.467
We have subtle and subtle ways of having egos

00:07:30.567 --> 00:07:34.267
like “I have come from this country, I must have ego,”

00:07:34.334 --> 00:07:38.067
“I come from this kind of family, I must have ego.”

00:07:38.133 --> 00:07:40.567
All kinds of stupid things they do,

00:07:40.634 --> 00:07:43.200
which are really sinful and they think

00:07:43.267 --> 00:07:46.167
they’re very great that they have ego.

00:07:46.234 --> 00:07:49.033
This ego, you have to fight,

00:07:49.100 --> 00:07:52.267
otherwise your resurrection is not possible,

00:07:52.334 --> 00:07:58.167
your attention cannot pass through the Agnya Chakra.

00:07:58.234 --> 00:08:01.634
As long as they have given us satanic identifications,

00:08:01.701 --> 00:08:05.100
it will not work out. It’s a very subtle happening

00:08:05.200 --> 00:08:10.567
— very, very subtle happening — that you should see your own ego.

00:08:10.634 --> 00:08:14.133
After Realisation I said, 'You know yourself.’

00:08:14.200 --> 00:08:17.501
The first thing you will know is that you have too much of

00:08:17.567 --> 00:08:20.501
conditioning and too much of ego.

00:08:21.234 --> 00:08:25.067
Like in India, I find people have so much conditioning

00:08:25.133 --> 00:08:29.200
of their so-called rituals — very ritualistic.

00:08:29.667 --> 00:08:34.167
Everything is a ritual with them and they cannot get out of it.

00:08:34.234 --> 00:08:36.367
That’s all the conditioning is,

00:08:36.434 --> 00:08:40.167
but ego is the worst part in the West, more in the West,

00:08:40.234 --> 00:08:43.267
where I don’t know what they think of themselves.

00:08:43.367 --> 00:08:46.467
In that ego they get lost.

00:08:46.567 --> 00:08:49.567
And they cannot see what’s wrong with them,

00:08:49.634 --> 00:08:53.267
with their own community, with their own people,

00:08:53.334 --> 00:08:56.601
who claim to be some, and such and such a thing.

00:08:56.667 --> 00:09:00.734
So this ego has really dominated so much.

00:09:00.801 --> 00:09:05.734
So far in the history, so many countries, nations, have been

00:09:05.801 --> 00:09:10.567
really tortured and butchered because of the ego of some people.

00:09:10.634 --> 00:09:15.634
Once they will realise

00:09:15.701 --> 00:09:19.767
how horrible they have been, how satanic they have been,

00:09:20.000 --> 00:09:23.267
how aggressive they have been, they’ll give it up.

00:09:23.367 --> 00:09:26.567
But they have to realise and, for that, I said,

00:09:26.634 --> 00:09:29.033
'You have to have your resurrection.’

00:09:29.100 --> 00:09:32.501
Without the resurrection, you will not know at all,

00:09:32.567 --> 00:09:36.567
you’ll not be conscious of what wrong you have been doing.

00:09:36.667 --> 00:09:41.400
It is very, very surprising how people go on doing wrong things,

00:09:41.467 --> 00:09:44.567
advertise them and come out as egos.

00:09:46.334 --> 00:09:50.033
When I read the newspapers, I say,

00:09:50.100 --> 00:09:52.601
'These are all stupid people all around.’

00:09:52.667 --> 00:09:56.033
— absolutely very, very

00:09:57.734 --> 00:10:01.434
stupid in the sense that they have no understanding

00:10:01.501 --> 00:10:05.200
of what they are doing. They are just killing people,

00:10:05.267 --> 00:10:10.067
enjoying the killing and they’re so violent it is impossible

00:10:10.133 --> 00:10:14.601
to understand what sort of life they are going to have

00:10:14.701 --> 00:10:17.434
after death – even before death.

00:10:18.300 --> 00:10:21.701
In this whole thing, you see the whole picture of the world.

00:10:21.767 --> 00:10:26.167
You’ll find all such countries who are still fighting for nonsense

00:10:26.234 --> 00:10:28.567
are very, very poor,

00:10:28.634 --> 00:10:31.167
are having very bad time

00:10:31.267 --> 00:10:36.334
and they are about to be completely finished.

00:10:36.434 --> 00:10:39.300
But they don’t want to see why they are suffering,

00:10:39.367 --> 00:10:43.000
why what’s happening, what is the problem.

00:10:43.100 --> 00:10:47.734
In the countries where there are affluence, lots of affluence,

00:10:47.801 --> 00:10:53.000
they also got lost. They too need resurrection.

00:10:54.200 --> 00:10:57.100
They have to rise above materialism

00:10:57.200 --> 00:11:01.200
and see for themselves what they’re doing is wrong.

00:11:01.801 --> 00:11:04.000
They are like, actually, cheats.

00:11:04.067 --> 00:11:06.734
They are cheating the society all the time.

00:11:06.801 --> 00:11:09.133
I think the whole economics is based

00:11:09.200 --> 00:11:13.133
on cheating, how you can cheat people. And in that cheating,

00:11:13.234 --> 00:11:16.167
you don’t even realise that you are doing something

00:11:16.234 --> 00:11:18.601
to make people so insecure.

00:11:18.701 --> 00:11:24.667
So this money business, also, is such that

00:11:24.734 --> 00:11:29.667
it makes you very greedy and you start giving too much importance to money.

00:11:32.634 --> 00:11:37.167
This is one thing to be understood from the life of Christ.

00:11:37.234 --> 00:11:43.234
He was a very simple, poor man, son of a carpenter.

00:11:44.667 --> 00:11:49.667
And to Him, money was nothing but an absolutely useless thing.

00:11:50.234 --> 00:11:52.534
To Him, Spirit was everything.

00:11:52.601 --> 00:11:55.634
And He was preaching and telling people

00:11:55.701 --> 00:11:59.634
that You must have spiritual awakening. Very important.

00:11:59.701 --> 00:12:03.133
Try to understand that there is life

00:12:03.200 --> 00:12:06.734
beyond all this and then you should get

00:12:06.801 --> 00:12:12.234
the best results out of this life,

00:12:12.334 --> 00:12:14.767
which you are just wasting.’

00:12:15.000 --> 00:12:17.300
He was so intelligent and

00:12:17.367 --> 00:12:23.067
the way He discussed with all those great fathers from the Church

00:12:23.133 --> 00:12:26.033
about the religion and all that,

00:12:26.100 --> 00:12:28.434
it’s amazing how a little boy

00:12:28.501 --> 00:12:33.067
could understand so deeply about religion.

00:12:34.534 --> 00:12:38.067
He was a small boy at that time, no doubt,

00:12:38.133 --> 00:12:44.067
but He was a person from the Divine, created by the Divine.

00:12:44.601 --> 00:12:49.434
He was Shri Ganesha. He’s Aum. He’s knowledge, everything.

00:12:49.501 --> 00:12:53.267
Despite that, nobody people recognised Him

00:12:53.334 --> 00:12:56.133
because they cannot recognise the Truth.

00:12:56.200 --> 00:12:59.033
They cannot understand the Truth.

00:12:59.133 --> 00:13:02.767
They are so stupid that they can only

00:13:03.000 --> 00:13:06.501
take to something that is falsehood, that is bad.

00:13:06.601 --> 00:13:10.200
And ultimately they crucified Him.

00:13:10.267 --> 00:13:14.133
This is a funny world where saints are crucified

00:13:14.234 --> 00:13:18.067
and the devils are given so much importance.

00:13:18.667 --> 00:13:20.801
But now the time has come

00:13:21.067 --> 00:13:25.534
for all these people who are doing wrong,

00:13:25.601 --> 00:13:30.667
who are trying to strangle others, will be strangled.

00:13:30.734 --> 00:13:35.300
They will be all exposed.I’ve told you this is the year of exposure.

00:13:35.367 --> 00:13:39.534
They’ll be all exposed if they are doing all such things

00:13:39.601 --> 00:13:42.300
of aggression and of greed.

00:13:42.400 --> 00:13:46.133
All their greed will be completely exposed

00:13:46.200 --> 00:13:48.334
and they will be thrown into hell.

00:13:48.400 --> 00:13:52.267
This is what I felt for this year especially.

00:13:52.334 --> 00:13:56.634
This has to happen, so best thing is to take to your resurrection,

00:13:56.701 --> 00:14:00.234
take to your higher life

00:14:00.334 --> 00:14:03.234
and see for yourself 'What are you doing?’

00:14:03.334 --> 00:14:06.033
What is the greatest thing to have?

00:14:06.100 --> 00:14:10.200
Money? Power? It doesn’t help anyone.

00:14:10.767 --> 00:14:13.300
People don’t have great name with that.

00:14:13.400 --> 00:14:16.801
Nobody remembers anybody who’s a drunkard.

00:14:17.033 --> 00:14:20.634
They don’t have statues of the drunkard people.

00:14:22.601 --> 00:14:26.300
So who achieves something higher?

00:14:26.367 --> 00:14:31.367
Who achieves great name like Christ?

00:14:32.267 --> 00:14:36.000
Those who have sacrificed their lives

00:14:36.067 --> 00:14:40.234
for the betterment of humanity, for helping them.

00:14:40.334 --> 00:14:42.267
Why did they do it?

00:14:43.133 --> 00:14:46.267
Because they loved human beings.

00:14:46.367 --> 00:14:49.100
They loved human being.

00:14:49.200 --> 00:14:53.133
When you love others, then you start thinking about

00:14:53.234 --> 00:14:57.567
‘what is the best, what can you do the best for them?’

00:14:57.667 --> 00:15:00.267
Now there are parents who are ignorant.

00:15:00.367 --> 00:15:03.567
They don’t know what to do for their children,

00:15:03.667 --> 00:15:09.100
so they try to dazzle the children with

00:15:09.567 --> 00:15:13.601
lots of things and food and this and that.

00:15:13.701 --> 00:15:17.400
But children, if they are not brought up with love,

00:15:17.501 --> 00:15:22.133
they’ll have no consideration whatsoever.They’ll go astray.

00:15:23.200 --> 00:15:26.634
But, in case they know somebody loves,

00:15:26.734 --> 00:15:29.601
for that love’s sake they will not go astray.

00:15:29.667 --> 00:15:31.501
They will not do wrong things.

00:15:31.567 --> 00:15:33.767
So the greatest thing about

00:15:34.000 --> 00:15:38.367
Christ or anyone of these great people is that they loved.

00:15:38.434 --> 00:15:43.167
They loved the people. They loved all human beings.

00:15:44.400 --> 00:15:46.567
That is what we have to know.

00:15:46.667 --> 00:15:50.634
Do we love ourselves, only our families,

00:15:50.734 --> 00:15:55.133
only our country? Or [do] we love the whole world?

00:15:56.200 --> 00:16:01.200
Do we live for the whole world or we live only for our limited circles.

00:16:01.701 --> 00:16:05.367
We should find out 'What are our aspirations?

00:16:05.467 --> 00:16:09.400
What are our desires? What do we want to have?’

00:16:10.033 --> 00:16:14.033
If you are really thinking of other people

00:16:15.334 --> 00:16:18.133
as your own, with love,

00:16:18.200 --> 00:16:23.200
it’s so joy giving. You may have any amount of ornaments,

00:16:23.267 --> 00:16:27.234
may have any amount of houses, any property, any money,

00:16:27.334 --> 00:16:29.234
you may have any power,

00:16:29.334 --> 00:16:32.133
you might be the prime minister of this

00:16:32.200 --> 00:16:34.601
or the prime minister of another,

00:16:34.667 --> 00:16:37.634
but if you have no love for others,

00:16:37.701 --> 00:16:40.133
you cannot enjoy yourself.

00:16:40.200 --> 00:16:43.234
Your enjoyment only comes through love,

00:16:43.334 --> 00:16:45.767
that your capacity to love.

00:16:46.033 --> 00:16:49.167
There’s no other way you can enjoy yourself.

00:16:49.234 --> 00:16:52.767
You may have television, you may have music

00:16:53.000 --> 00:16:55.467
you may go for dinner parties, everything,

00:16:55.534 --> 00:16:58.434
but still nothing penetrates.

00:16:59.200 --> 00:17:03.234
Nothing is there to give you real joy.

00:17:03.334 --> 00:17:05.567
That’s what Christ has taught us,

00:17:05.634 --> 00:17:09.267
that He had love for all the human beings

00:17:09.334 --> 00:17:13.601
and He wanted to prepare them for the Resurrection.

00:17:14.634 --> 00:17:18.167
He came before Sahaja Yoga came in.

00:17:18.234 --> 00:17:21.334
If He had not done that job,

00:17:22.067 --> 00:17:25.133
it would have been difficult for Me to achieve it.

00:17:25.234 --> 00:17:28.234
So He had prepared the stage for Sahaja Yoga.

00:17:28.334 --> 00:17:32.167
That now your Agnyas are opened

00:17:32.234 --> 00:17:37.567
and through the Agnya you can take the Kundalini upward

00:17:37.667 --> 00:17:43.100
through the Sahasrara and open the fontanel bone area.

00:17:43.200 --> 00:17:49.400
All this He thought of was a part and parcel of His love for people.

00:17:49.501 --> 00:17:53.267
And that’s what He did. And He cared for so many people.

00:17:53.334 --> 00:17:56.133
He’s such a help to us in Sahaja Yoga.

00:17:56.234 --> 00:17:58.100
Without Him, I don’t know

00:17:58.167 --> 00:18:01.801
how could I have really broken the Agnya Chakra.

00:18:02.801 --> 00:18:06.801
Because, as you know, Agnya is such a horrible thing.

00:18:07.033 --> 00:18:10.033
People go on doing wrong things through Agnya

00:18:10.100 --> 00:18:12.767
and they never feel bad about it,

00:18:13.000 --> 00:18:15.367
never think they have done anything wrong,

00:18:15.467 --> 00:18:18.767
they have harmed anyone, they have tortured anybody

00:18:19.000 --> 00:18:20.767
or they have made others cry.

00:18:21.000 --> 00:18:25.501
They go on with their Agnya, but they have no heart

00:18:25.567 --> 00:18:29.133
to feel what they have been up to.

00:18:29.200 --> 00:18:33.334
It’s Christ only. He shows us that you break your Agnya,

00:18:33.434 --> 00:18:35.367
pass through your Agnya.

00:18:35.467 --> 00:18:37.467
Here they call it as a third eye.

00:18:37.567 --> 00:18:40.667
The other day one lady came with a magazine of 'Third Eye’

00:18:40.734 --> 00:18:43.701
and when I told her what it is she was surprised.

00:18:43.767 --> 00:18:46.534
If your third eye is to be opened means

00:18:46.601 --> 00:18:50.667
Christ is to be awakened within you, on your Agnya.

00:18:50.734 --> 00:18:54.667
That’s the third eye. Now what He does by —

00:18:54.767 --> 00:18:58.167
He creates a witness state within you.

00:18:58.234 --> 00:19:01.067
You become the witness of the whole drama.

00:19:01.133 --> 00:19:03.300
You start seeing the whole drama

00:19:03.400 --> 00:19:07.567
and you are amazed how you are silent,

00:19:07.667 --> 00:19:10.133
thoughtlessly aware

00:19:10.234 --> 00:19:14.167
and how you are seeing everything without reacting.

00:19:14.234 --> 00:19:18.267
This is where we have to believe that Christ has taken

00:19:18.367 --> 00:19:21.334
His form in our Agnya.

00:19:21.434 --> 00:19:23.267
His birth is there.

00:19:23.334 --> 00:19:25.167
His resurrection is there,

00:19:25.234 --> 00:19:29.000
all that we have got it already, worked it out.

00:19:29.067 --> 00:19:33.000
Like a machinery, the whole being’s made

00:19:33.067 --> 00:19:36.367
and we have different, different chakras and centres.

00:19:36.467 --> 00:19:39.267
This is the last, most difficult centre,

00:19:39.334 --> 00:19:45.567
which was really opened out by Jesus Christ.

00:19:45.634 --> 00:19:50.200
He’s the one who dared it and who did it so beautifully

00:19:50.267 --> 00:19:55.234
that we too have now capacity to look at our ego,

00:19:55.300 --> 00:19:58.234
to see for ourselves, ‡What are we doing?

00:19:58.334 --> 00:20:02.767
Why do we think we are something very exceptional?’

00:20:03.000 --> 00:20:06.167
Once you start seeing the ego, you will be amazed.

00:20:06.234 --> 00:20:10.767
Whatever work you may do, whatever you may do, you’ll never be tired

00:20:11.000 --> 00:20:14.000
We get tired because all the time ego is saying,

00:20:14.100 --> 00:20:16.133
'Oh, you are so great.

00:20:16.234 --> 00:20:19.234
You are doing so much work for others.

00:20:19.334 --> 00:20:22.067
You have achieved so much,’ all that.

00:20:22.133 --> 00:20:26.100
So then the ego goes on all the time

00:20:26.167 --> 00:20:30.167
pointing out all this false greatness about us

00:20:30.234 --> 00:20:34.267
and we get tired that 'We are so great and why should we work?

00:20:34.334 --> 00:20:36.200
Why should we help others?’

00:20:36.300 --> 00:20:40.534
Like that, funny ideas start crawling in our mind

00:20:40.634 --> 00:20:46.000
and what we do is that we feel very tired out.

00:20:46.067 --> 00:20:49.267
Fighting with those ideas, we feel very tired.

00:20:49.334 --> 00:20:52.234
Now, our whole situation

00:20:53.334 --> 00:20:57.501
is made much simpler by the life of Christ.

00:20:57.567 --> 00:21:02.400
But look at the Christian nations. They are juxtaposition.

00:21:02.501 --> 00:21:06.601
They are on the other side of Christ’s teachings.

00:21:06.701 --> 00:21:10.000
They are the most aggressive countries.

00:21:10.067 --> 00:21:13.567
They aggress people so much

00:21:13.634 --> 00:21:17.267
that in the whole world they are regarded as something

00:21:17.334 --> 00:21:22.267
very great and like they’re the kings or something.

00:21:22.367 --> 00:21:26.534
I know this because we were in slavery in India

00:21:26.601 --> 00:21:30.400
and I was surprised that these people came from outside

00:21:30.467 --> 00:21:33.300
and were nicely become master.

00:21:33.400 --> 00:21:38.100
They were masters and used to treat us so badly,

00:21:38.200 --> 00:21:42.200
used to really make slaves out of us.

00:21:43.167 --> 00:21:50.000
So the slavery started and then all such things started in India,

00:21:50.067 --> 00:21:52.033
as well as abroad.

00:21:52.133 --> 00:21:54.567
Everywhere people started thinking

00:21:54.634 --> 00:21:57.367
that they are great – and they were Christians.

00:21:57.434 --> 00:22:01.467
They used to go to church and from the church what did you learn?

00:22:01.534 --> 00:22:05.033
How to dominate others, how to show them down,

00:22:05.100 --> 00:22:09.067
how to take away all that belongs

00:22:09.634 --> 00:22:14.067
to the poorer people or to the less stronger people.

00:22:14.133 --> 00:22:17.033
It’s a thing we have seen ourselves.

00:22:17.100 --> 00:22:22.234
So this happens to people who have this ego, very, very powerful.

00:22:22.300 --> 00:22:26.400
And they try to take over

00:22:26.467 --> 00:22:28.467
things that belong to other countries.

00:22:28.534 --> 00:22:31.801
What right have they got to take somebody’s country,

00:22:32.033 --> 00:22:34.000
I can’t understand.

00:22:56.667 --> 00:23:01.701
All these complications are there.

00:23:01.767 --> 00:23:05.200
In the modern time they’re the worst.

00:23:05.300 --> 00:23:08.300
It was never so bad as it is today.

00:23:08.400 --> 00:23:13.400
We had Hitler. We had people of that kind once in a while.

00:23:13.467 --> 00:23:16.667
But the whole world was together on one side.

00:23:16.767 --> 00:23:18.767
Nobody was confused.

00:23:19.567 --> 00:23:24.601
Nobody knew that you have to fight all the time.

00:23:24.701 --> 00:23:28.634
Now, maybe because of newspapers, I don’t know why,

00:23:28.701 --> 00:23:32.367
nobody knows which side is correct, which is not correct.

00:23:32.434 --> 00:23:35.534
It’s being such a dispute about everything

00:23:35.634 --> 00:23:39.701
and people don’t try to understand the reality of the problem.

00:23:39.767 --> 00:23:43.567
And they are killing left and right all kinds of people.

00:23:43.634 --> 00:23:46.534
It is very surprising how,

00:23:46.601 --> 00:23:49.701
in this world, human beings are killing

00:23:49.801 --> 00:23:53.300
each other much more than the animals do.

00:23:53.367 --> 00:23:57.634
We are the worst, worse than the animals,

00:23:57.734 --> 00:24:04.701
that we are killing ourselves, our own clan, our own people.

00:24:05.300 --> 00:24:08.567
In India also we are surprised how

00:24:08.634 --> 00:24:13.000
they are killing — Kashmiris are killing Kashmiris.

00:24:14.300 --> 00:24:16.767
In the same way, everywhere you go, you find

00:24:17.000 --> 00:24:19.033
they are fighting among themselves.

00:24:19.100 --> 00:24:21.567
If you go to Africa, you will be surprised how

00:24:21.634 --> 00:24:23.567
they are fighting among themselves.

00:24:23.634 --> 00:24:28.367
I mean, now the principle of fighting has come up very strong

00:24:28.434 --> 00:24:32.567
and people think fighting is a very important part of human beings.

00:24:32.634 --> 00:24:36.634
Anything you say, immediately fighting will start.

00:24:36.701 --> 00:24:40.534
Now look at Christ and His life.

00:24:40.634 --> 00:24:44.567
He didn’t fight anyone. He didn’t argue with anyone

00:24:44.634 --> 00:24:49.701
and He accepted, accepted the death on the cross.

00:24:51.000 --> 00:24:53.767
He accepted it because He knew

00:24:54.033 --> 00:24:56.400
that it is for the resurrection,

00:24:56.467 --> 00:25:00.067
for not only His, [but] for the resurrection of the whole world.

00:25:00.167 --> 00:25:02.267
And this is what we have to learn.

00:25:02.334 --> 00:25:05.400
We have to be the models of resurrection.

00:25:05.501 --> 00:25:08.067
We see all these things happening,

00:25:08.167 --> 00:25:10.601
we’re upset also about it

00:25:10.701 --> 00:25:13.767
and when after Realisation

00:25:14.033 --> 00:25:17.534
people see that surroundings are full of this,

00:25:17.601 --> 00:25:20.534
their own people are like this, they start fighting

00:25:20.601 --> 00:25:24.300
for nothing at all and they realise

00:25:24.367 --> 00:25:28.133
that 'These are my own people who are doing this nonsense.’

00:25:28.200 --> 00:25:31.167
You can’t correct it. You can’t do anything.

00:25:31.234 --> 00:25:35.634
But if your Agnya is clear, if your ego is finished,

00:25:35.701 --> 00:25:42.067
if there is no domination of any kind in your mind

00:25:43.067 --> 00:25:46.200
– and also [if] your conditioning is finished,

00:25:46.267 --> 00:25:50.601
then you become the channel of creating peace.

00:25:51.601 --> 00:25:56.167
You are the one, wherever you are, you can create peace.

00:25:56.234 --> 00:26:00.667
This is something, a special thing for Sahaja Yogis to know,

00:26:00.767 --> 00:26:05.234
that if you have no Agnya, you may look like you are suffering,

00:26:05.300 --> 00:26:08.534
but you are not. You are doing it for others,

00:26:08.601 --> 00:26:13.567
for surroundings, for your friends, for your neighbours,

00:26:13.634 --> 00:26:16.701
you can say for your countrymen, for all of them.

00:26:16.767 --> 00:26:19.501
When you have no Agnya

00:26:19.567 --> 00:26:24.267
you become such a big source of Divine Force

00:26:24.334 --> 00:26:27.667
that it can work out anything.

00:26:27.734 --> 00:26:31.167
It can change, transform people.

00:26:32.701 --> 00:26:36.467
It can happen like that and

00:26:36.534 --> 00:26:39.634
it has happened to many people before, individually.

00:26:39.701 --> 00:26:43.667
But now collectively I’m sure all this anger,

00:26:43.767 --> 00:26:46.734
all this temperament of aggression

00:26:47.000 --> 00:26:49.434
and all these challenges

00:26:49.501 --> 00:26:53.434
from all these nasty people can be brought to an end.

00:26:54.267 --> 00:26:57.801
with the people who have no ego,

00:26:58.501 --> 00:27:03.601
with the people who are not justifying their wrong things,

00:27:03.701 --> 00:27:09.701
with the people who have a clear cut idea as to what is the Truth.

00:27:11.000 --> 00:27:14.567
They may speak. They may not speak. It makes no difference.

00:27:14.634 --> 00:27:18.567
Whatever they are, but they are such a big shield

00:27:18.634 --> 00:27:20.767
against those aggressive forces,

00:27:21.000 --> 00:27:24.000
which are ruining the peace of the world.

00:27:24.100 --> 00:27:26.667
So Christ did it for the peace,

00:27:26.734 --> 00:27:28.734
to bring peace on this Earth.

00:27:29.000 --> 00:27:32.334
It’s very important there should be peace,

00:27:32.400 --> 00:27:35.734
but if there is no peace within, how can you have peace outside.

00:27:36.000 --> 00:27:39.033
It’s very surprising how so many countries

00:27:39.133 --> 00:27:43.234
who talk of peace are engaged in wars and fighting.

00:27:43.334 --> 00:27:45.567
How can you have like that?

00:27:45.634 --> 00:27:48.534
They have no solution. They don’t understand.

00:27:48.601 --> 00:27:54.667
The only solution I find is to transform them in Sahaja Yoga.

00:27:54.767 --> 00:27:56.501
That’s the only one.

00:27:56.601 --> 00:27:58.767
You have to take out their ego.

00:27:59.033 --> 00:28:01.767
You can see in many people, it resists.

00:28:02.000 --> 00:28:03.801
It is there, is working.

00:28:04.067 --> 00:28:08.567
This ego is a very, very dangerous thing people have.

00:28:09.434 --> 00:28:12.701
So this one was the one

00:28:12.801 --> 00:28:17.801
which was really handled by Jesus.

00:28:18.033 --> 00:28:21.701
He tried to neutralise your ego.

00:28:25.400 --> 00:28:31.501
He tried to take out the problems of the ego

00:28:32.367 --> 00:28:36.067
to make you a humble, mild personality.

00:28:36.133 --> 00:28:39.067
To say that a humble and mild person

00:28:39.133 --> 00:28:43.634
is always into a danger is a wrong thing to say.

00:28:44.334 --> 00:28:49.334
See them. When the people are aggressive

00:28:50.100 --> 00:28:52.767
and people are trying to dominate,

00:28:53.567 --> 00:28:57.567
the humble man is the winner, not the one who dominates.

00:29:22.267 --> 00:29:29.167
So main thing is now to watch out for

00:29:29.601 --> 00:29:33.567
your Mr. Ego, how it works. It’s very interesting,

00:29:33.667 --> 00:29:36.701
very interesting to see how it makes a drama.

00:29:37.334 --> 00:29:39.367
how it tries to cover up things,

00:29:40.000 --> 00:29:43.501
how he tries to show that you are superior to others.

00:29:43.601 --> 00:29:48.100
It is to be seen. It is to be seen very clearly

00:29:48.167 --> 00:29:51.767
what this Agnya is up to.

00:29:52.667 --> 00:29:56.067
It’s a very, very mischievous thing,

00:29:56.167 --> 00:30:00.167
very harmful thing and most embarrassing also.

00:30:00.601 --> 00:30:03.334
So these egoistical people are

00:30:03.400 --> 00:30:07.367
like that and ultimately they become nervous people

00:30:07.434 --> 00:30:11.100
— very nervous and think no end of themselves.

00:30:11.167 --> 00:30:13.801
First they try to control others.

00:30:14.033 --> 00:30:18.300
But then they are needed to be controlled they are like that

00:30:18.767 --> 00:30:23.067
because they are all the time trying to control others

00:30:23.167 --> 00:30:27.067
and they don’t know how to control themselves.

00:30:28.467 --> 00:30:31.400
Who is the child crying so much?

00:30:31.501 --> 00:30:33.701
Why is he crying?

00:30:43.767 --> 00:30:45.767
Must be something wrong.

00:30:49.300 --> 00:30:53.033
Normally children keep very quiet in my lecture.

00:31:03.067 --> 00:31:06.100
Now this ego is also like this child.

00:31:07.234 --> 00:31:10.400
It doesn’t hear anything, doesn’t understand anything.

00:31:10.501 --> 00:31:13.534
It just goes on disturbing everything.

00:31:14.300 --> 00:31:17.000
In the same way, our ego also behaves,

00:31:17.067 --> 00:31:20.234
without having any collective knowledge, without having

00:31:20.334 --> 00:31:23.634
'What are you up to? What you are doing?

00:31:23.701 --> 00:31:27.801
Who, are you harming?’ Nothing, just a satisfaction,

00:31:28.033 --> 00:31:31.601
such a blind satisfaction that you are doing something

00:31:31.667 --> 00:31:34.200
to assert your personality.

00:31:34.267 --> 00:31:37.234
You see, if you just watch your ego, you’ll laugh

00:31:37.334 --> 00:31:40.367
and enjoy the buffoon, you’ll see what a thing it is.

00:31:40.467 --> 00:31:42.567
‘It has been befooling me so much,

00:31:42.667 --> 00:31:47.133
what a horrible thing this ego was.’

00:31:47.234 --> 00:31:49.300
At the time when Christ was there,

00:31:49.400 --> 00:31:51.634
the people have such a lot of ego.

00:31:51.734 --> 00:31:55.267
Nobody talked about it. Nobody said anything.

00:31:56.234 --> 00:31:59.300
So this was the best way that He could show us

00:31:59.400 --> 00:32:03.534
that you can break your Agnya by sacrificing your life

00:32:03.634 --> 00:32:06.801
— not in Sahaja Yoga, not in Sahaja Yoga.

00:32:07.067 --> 00:32:09.434
But in a way, in Sahaja Yoga also,

00:32:09.501 --> 00:32:13.567
if you have an ego you should first of all have witness state.

00:32:13.634 --> 00:32:16.534
It’s the other way round. If you have ego,

00:32:16.601 --> 00:32:20.300
you cannot have witness state. If you cannot have witness state,

00:32:20.367 --> 00:32:25.534
you cannot improve your ego. It’s a very confusing thing.

00:32:25.634 --> 00:32:29.667
Now supposing you develop a very big ego,

00:32:31.434 --> 00:32:34.400
then you go on justifying it all the time.

00:32:34.467 --> 00:32:37.734
You think, ‘Whatever I have done is good. After all,

00:32:37.801 --> 00:32:40.501
it’s very good for everyone, good for me.’

00:32:40.567 --> 00:32:42.667
Self certification starts.

00:32:42.734 --> 00:32:45.334
With that, you can never see

00:32:45.400 --> 00:32:47.767
what you are doing to yourself,

00:32:48.000 --> 00:32:50.000
what you are doing to others.

00:32:50.067 --> 00:32:54.067
It’s something, such a blind-folded nonsense.

00:32:54.133 --> 00:32:58.000
When this ego comes up in that way,

00:32:58.067 --> 00:33:03.067
then, I mean, we can have Hitlers, we can have all kinds of things.

00:33:03.133 --> 00:33:07.501
Any small point they take and form a group of people

00:33:07.567 --> 00:33:10.501
doing this kind of thing – anything.

00:33:10.601 --> 00:33:14.701
They will say that ‘Now, we are people who are spiritual.

00:33:14.767 --> 00:33:18.067
So we have a group and we are spiritual people

00:33:18.133 --> 00:33:21.167
and whatever we do is the right.’

00:33:21.234 --> 00:33:26.300
But who says it is right? By what law is it right?

00:33:26.400 --> 00:33:30.133
And we have had so many cults and this like that,

00:33:30.234 --> 00:33:33.634
everywhere, where people joined them, kill themselves,

00:33:33.701 --> 00:33:38.100
had all kinds of problems. How can that be spirituality?

00:33:38.200 --> 00:33:42.300
In spirituality the first and foremost thing is

00:33:42.400 --> 00:33:47.234
that the person becomes very meek, very humble,

00:33:48.734 --> 00:33:53.734
very humble. His heart — humility is the power.

00:33:54.767 --> 00:33:58.534
His humility is the one that works

00:33:58.634 --> 00:34:01.634
and his humility is the one that glorifies.

00:34:02.400 --> 00:34:05.033
It is not the aggression.

00:34:05.100 --> 00:34:09.634
See, Hitler came and died. Who worships him?

00:34:09.701 --> 00:34:14.534
Others also came. Like Mussolini came, died. Who worships?

00:34:14.601 --> 00:34:18.033
There are so many like that who came and went away.

00:34:18.100 --> 00:34:23.400
They don’t even want to have their statues, so bad as they were.

00:34:23.501 --> 00:34:28.367
So those who have this ego are really very stupid people

00:34:28.434 --> 00:34:31.100
in the sense that they do all wrong,

00:34:31.167 --> 00:34:33.534
thinking it is the right thing to do.

00:34:33.634 --> 00:34:37.634
Ultimately, they are recognised as absolutely

00:34:38.567 --> 00:34:41.467
very, very wrong type of people.

00:34:43.167 --> 00:34:46.200
People don’t want to take their names even.

00:34:46.300 --> 00:34:50.367
So the time can prove what are they and what they’re doing.

00:34:51.434 --> 00:34:57.267
It’s a very, very calculated work of the Divine.

00:34:58.667 --> 00:35:02.133
You shouldn’t play into the hands of your ego.

00:35:02.200 --> 00:35:05.701
Try to see yourself. ‘Oh, Mr Ego, so you are there.’

00:35:05.801 --> 00:35:11.367
Try to watch. And that time, if you take the name of Jesus,

00:35:11.434 --> 00:35:15.033
ego will go away. Just say

00:35:16.501 --> 00:35:22.300
the mantra of Jesus and ego will disappear.

00:35:25.267 --> 00:35:32.334
Another side of this horrible ego is the conditioning.

00:35:33.267 --> 00:35:37.267
That also has a very, very, very subtle ego.

00:35:38.033 --> 00:35:43.033
For example, supposing if somebody comes to your house

00:35:44.067 --> 00:35:48.467
and starts saying that ‘Ah, what a dirty carpet.

00:35:49.133 --> 00:35:52.400
I don’t like this colour. That thing I don’t like’

00:35:52.501 --> 00:35:56.367
without understanding that you are hurting another person.

00:35:56.434 --> 00:35:59.367
Talking like that, he comes inside.

00:35:59.467 --> 00:36:04.400
And then, you see how stupid he has been

00:36:04.467 --> 00:36:08.467
because nobody likes such a person who is talking like that.

00:36:08.567 --> 00:36:11.334
But to him, it is very important

00:36:11.400 --> 00:36:16.133
that he should correct because he has a conditioning

00:36:16.200 --> 00:36:19.267
that a particular type of carpet is good,

00:36:19.334 --> 00:36:23.234
the another is not. That conditioning works.

00:36:23.334 --> 00:36:25.434
And he goes on talking nonsense

00:36:25.534 --> 00:36:29.167
that ‘This is not good, that is not good.’

00:36:38.667 --> 00:36:41.267
You cannot enjoy anything.

00:36:41.334 --> 00:36:43.634
You cannot enjoy anything.

00:36:43.701 --> 00:36:48.267
You go to any home, you don’t like it because there’s conditioning.

00:36:48.334 --> 00:36:51.033
You know of something else which is good.

00:36:51.133 --> 00:36:53.367
No – so they can’t enjoy.

00:36:53.434 --> 00:36:57.434
Everything they decide on their conditioning.

00:36:57.534 --> 00:37:00.234
[There] Is nothing independent.

00:37:00.300 --> 00:37:04.434
It has nothing to do with the intrinsic personality.

00:37:04.534 --> 00:37:07.467
Intrinsic value of that thing.

00:37:08.200 --> 00:37:12.701
Just like that, 'Oh, I don’t like it.’ It’s not good.

00:37:12.767 --> 00:37:16.067
It should not be said by Sahaja Yogis.

00:37:16.133 --> 00:37:18.601
Never use this word.

00:37:18.667 --> 00:37:22.334
You can find out from Me. I never do that.

00:37:22.400 --> 00:37:25.467
Whatever it is I say, it’s all right.

00:37:25.567 --> 00:37:28.000
I never criticize it.

00:37:28.100 --> 00:37:31.734
This criticism business comes from this conditioning

00:37:31.801 --> 00:37:34.367
because you have had such conditioning.

00:37:34.434 --> 00:37:38.200
Supposing you are an Englishman you have English conditioning.

00:37:38.267 --> 00:37:42.667
Now, correction comes.

00:37:43.334 --> 00:37:47.300
Their cows got this disease.

00:37:48.067 --> 00:37:53.334
How did they get the disease when you are such perfect people?

00:37:53.434 --> 00:37:57.534
Then in Europe the animals got one disease.

00:37:57.601 --> 00:37:59.300
How is it they got

00:37:59.367 --> 00:38:04.767
this disease when you think you are the cleanest people living ever?

00:38:05.000 --> 00:38:07.100
Just watch out why?

00:38:07.167 --> 00:38:09.567
It’s all their own conditioning

00:38:09.634 --> 00:38:14.100
that ‘We know everything. We are the best in the whole world

00:38:14.167 --> 00:38:18.667
and we have a right to rule everyone.’ Now have it.

00:38:18.734 --> 00:38:23.467
Now those who were very rich people, like America and all that,

00:38:23.567 --> 00:38:26.200
used to think no end of themselves.

00:38:26.267 --> 00:38:28.601
Now what has happened?

00:38:28.701 --> 00:38:34.167
Suddenly it has become a country where everybody has to pity.

00:38:34.267 --> 00:38:37.601
Why? What is the reason? Why suddenly it has happened?

00:38:37.701 --> 00:38:41.601
It’s always the nature which corrects you

00:38:41.667 --> 00:38:44.334
by giving the other side of it.

00:38:45.033 --> 00:38:47.467
Anything you try to boast of

00:38:47.567 --> 00:38:51.167
or you try to put your conditioning of others, it repels,

00:38:51.234 --> 00:38:52.734
it comes up on you.

00:38:53.701 --> 00:38:57.634
It works in such a great manner that you can’t imagine.

00:38:58.501 --> 00:39:02.267
And then it does not work out,

00:39:02.367 --> 00:39:07.667
then there are earthquakes. All kinds of calamities come in.

00:39:08.701 --> 00:39:13.167
There were a group of people who were white-skinned

00:39:13.267 --> 00:39:19.133
near the River Mississippi. And they were called as rednecks

00:39:19.200 --> 00:39:22.200
because it was always hot, their necks were always hot,

00:39:22.267 --> 00:39:26.067
they were such angry, hot-tempered people.

00:39:26.133 --> 00:39:30.234
And these rednecks were known to be very cruel.

00:39:30.300 --> 00:39:34.300
They used to kill people and put the blame on some other

00:39:34.367 --> 00:39:40.267
people from aboriginal people and arrest them and destroy them.

00:39:40.334 --> 00:39:43.000
It went on and on and on.

00:39:43.067 --> 00:39:46.734
But one day this Mississippi got flooded,

00:39:46.801 --> 00:39:52.734
so much flooded it entered all the houses of these rednecks, you see

00:39:52.801 --> 00:39:54.801
and I saw them running away

00:39:55.033 --> 00:39:58.334
with all their belongings which they could not carry also.

00:39:58.400 --> 00:40:01.501
Some of they were leaving behind, some they were running

00:40:01.567 --> 00:40:04.200
and, while running also, they were losing it.

00:40:04.300 --> 00:40:07.467
Like that, the whole chaos took place of these rednecks.

00:40:07.534 --> 00:40:10.734
And now, I am told, they are much better.

00:40:10.801 --> 00:40:15.467
All that nonsense they had of killing all the black people and

00:40:15.534 --> 00:40:18.467
torturing them, now has come on their heads.

00:40:18.534 --> 00:40:20.801
Mississippi has taught them a lesson.

00:40:21.067 --> 00:40:25.567
So how the nature also doesn’t like conditioned people

00:40:25.634 --> 00:40:30.634
— conditioning is creating a big problem now, even now,

00:40:30.701 --> 00:40:34.467
in all the countries, like racialism.

00:40:34.567 --> 00:40:38.300
Racialism is a very bad conditioning.

00:40:38.367 --> 00:40:42.567
I mean, if somebody’s black or white or red, what does it matter?

00:40:42.634 --> 00:40:45.300
God has made that person.

00:40:45.400 --> 00:40:47.767
I always say that in America,

00:40:48.000 --> 00:40:51.033
if they remove all the people who are not white-skinned,

00:40:51.100 --> 00:40:53.400
what will be left there?

00:40:53.467 --> 00:40:57.033
They don’t know how to sing,. They don’t know how to play.

00:40:57.100 --> 00:40:59.801
They don’t know how to operate.

00:41:00.033 --> 00:41:03.367
All the Indian doctors and Indian nurses will come away

00:41:03.467 --> 00:41:05.601
and what will they do?

00:41:05.701 --> 00:41:09.601
Imagine, thinking no end of themselves, they are great racists.

00:41:09.667 --> 00:41:13.334
Even now, they are, but gradually they’ll definitely improve

00:41:13.400 --> 00:41:16.100
because they should know their deficiencies.

00:41:16.167 --> 00:41:20.200
This world is one and you need people from every country

00:41:20.267 --> 00:41:23.267
to help each other. But this conditioning of

00:41:23.334 --> 00:41:25.701
thinking themselves to be something great

00:41:25.767 --> 00:41:29.767
the very bad conditioning. It is the mixture of ego

00:41:30.000 --> 00:41:33.467
with conditioning, conditioning giving the ego

00:41:34.434 --> 00:41:36.634
that ‘we are the best.’

00:41:36.734 --> 00:41:41.434
But I am very happy to know that after Realisation,

00:41:41.501 --> 00:41:45.467
it so happens, with this resurrection,

00:41:45.534 --> 00:41:50.534
Sahaja Yogis start thinking, understanding

00:41:51.567 --> 00:41:55.234
what is wrong in their own community,

00:41:55.334 --> 00:41:59.801
what is the mistake they have been committing.

00:42:00.067 --> 00:42:03.133
They just become like that — alert.

00:42:03.200 --> 00:42:05.033
And they start telling

00:42:05.100 --> 00:42:08.334
they are the ones who are doing this kind of nonsense.

00:42:08.400 --> 00:42:11.133
Imagine. It is very surprising

00:42:11.200 --> 00:42:15.467
how you become conscious of the defects of your own country.

00:42:15.567 --> 00:42:17.501
It is so important, is Agnya.

00:42:17.567 --> 00:42:20.634
That’s what I think Christ had realised,

00:42:20.701 --> 00:42:24.367
that Agnya should break. Unless and until Agnya breaks,

00:42:24.467 --> 00:42:29.000
people cannot go further. And that’s why He crucified Himself

00:42:29.067 --> 00:42:33.100
and then resurrected because without killing the Agnya,

00:42:33.167 --> 00:42:35.300
you cannot resurrect.

00:42:35.400 --> 00:42:39.467
All these things have worked out so well now

00:42:39.567 --> 00:42:44.367
that the whole world is seeing you like a panoramic view,

00:42:45.067 --> 00:42:49.534
of complete destruction of the nonsense.

00:42:50.634 --> 00:42:53.033
They are seeing this very clearly

00:42:53.100 --> 00:42:57.200
and you see now these people who would not even look at us,

00:42:57.300 --> 00:43:03.167
who had a very stiff nose and stiff lips and stiff neck

00:43:03.234 --> 00:43:08.634
— all is relaxed. They are wondering why this is happening.

00:43:08.701 --> 00:43:11.334
‘From when did we get this curse?’

00:43:11.400 --> 00:43:14.234
So for the Europeans specially,

00:43:14.300 --> 00:43:17.734
they have to understand the beauty

00:43:17.801 --> 00:43:22.133
and the love and the greatness of other human beings

00:43:22.200 --> 00:43:26.133
and then that will so much satisfy them.

00:43:27.100 --> 00:43:32.367
Why there is so much problem now of this recession, how it has come.

00:43:32.434 --> 00:43:36.734
Recession is nothing. It is the same Mr. Ego.

00:43:36.801 --> 00:43:43.067
It is the same conditioning, which was like a snake was eating up.

00:43:43.167 --> 00:43:46.067
Now it has receded. It is full.

00:43:46.133 --> 00:43:48.801
It doesn’t need any more. It’s quite full.

00:43:49.033 --> 00:43:54.701
And maybe it is now in danger of getting indigestion, I think.

00:43:54.767 --> 00:44:00.067
So that these two snakes that were eating human beings are receding.

00:44:01.133 --> 00:44:04.767
It’s the best time where you can see the drama.

00:44:05.000 --> 00:44:09.200
Drama of ego and your conditioning.

00:44:09.300 --> 00:44:13.467
How these two things have eaten up human beings.

00:44:13.534 --> 00:44:15.734
One should feel shy.

00:44:15.801 --> 00:44:20.534
One should feel a little bit modest about it.

00:44:20.601 --> 00:44:25.501
When you are full of ego, you don’t even see anything.

00:44:25.567 --> 00:44:31.033
Or putting a conditioning on others, it’s horrible, I tell you.

00:44:31.100 --> 00:44:36.434
I can’t understand how can they put a conditioning on others.

00:44:36.534 --> 00:44:41.534
It is now, you people all enjoy, say, for Indian music.

00:44:42.133 --> 00:44:44.467
But when the British were ruling us,

00:44:44.534 --> 00:44:48.767
they used to think it's a horrible noise going on.

00:44:49.000 --> 00:44:51.167
They could never understand.

00:44:51.234 --> 00:44:56.000
Now they are paying such a lot to attend the program for music.

00:44:56.100 --> 00:44:59.367
That is also a kind of a rebuff, but

00:44:59.434 --> 00:45:03.100
also they don’t understand. Still they will go

00:45:03.167 --> 00:45:07.767
because it’s regarded as a very big fashion

00:45:08.033 --> 00:45:10.267
to listen to Indian music.

00:45:10.334 --> 00:45:14.601
So it is your ego also is so stupid

00:45:14.701 --> 00:45:17.067
that God knows when it will give in.

00:45:17.167 --> 00:45:19.601
Today it will say, ‘This is the best thing.’

00:45:19.667 --> 00:45:21.667
Tomorrow it will say, 'No, no, no, no.

00:45:21.734 --> 00:45:24.634
We should take the other one. That’s much better.’

00:45:24.734 --> 00:45:27.734
Indecisive, they have no discrimination.

00:45:27.801 --> 00:45:31.200
Basically, people have no discrimination.

00:45:31.267 --> 00:45:34.434
Those who have ego are indiscriminate.

00:45:35.067 --> 00:45:39.067
They cannot discriminate between evil and good.

00:45:39.167 --> 00:45:42.133
And such people have been now,

00:45:42.701 --> 00:45:45.734
thank God, have been punished quite a lot.

00:45:46.000 --> 00:45:50.167
But it is the life of Christ, His model,

00:45:50.267 --> 00:45:57.000
proves that your resurrection is so essential,

00:45:57.100 --> 00:46:02.767
which is so innate, that unless and until you get it, you are lost.

00:46:03.534 --> 00:46:07.234
Whether it’s a country, whether it’s a person

00:46:07.300 --> 00:46:11.367
or any organisation. This ego that you have

00:46:11.467 --> 00:46:14.400
can ruin, ultimately, is now been proved,

00:46:15.267 --> 00:46:19.367
can completely take you away from reality.

00:46:19.467 --> 00:46:22.267
That is the thing that blinds you,

00:46:22.334 --> 00:46:25.234
which can — another ego can blind you also.

00:46:25.300 --> 00:46:28.267
Like we have those priests, we have those mullahs

00:46:28.334 --> 00:46:32.400
and all these people. They are the ones who have this

00:46:33.300 --> 00:46:37.300
tremendous power to misguide

00:46:38.100 --> 00:46:42.400
you because your ego has no discretion sense.

00:46:42.467 --> 00:46:45.400
It doesn’t even think like that.

00:46:45.467 --> 00:46:47.667
And when they are specially,

00:46:47.734 --> 00:46:51.267
not so much on the ego side, but on the conditioning side,

00:46:51.334 --> 00:46:54.667
it’s even much worse – much worse.

00:46:54.734 --> 00:46:57.601
Because when you are conditioned,

00:46:57.701 --> 00:47:00.634
you start believing into all kinds of nonsense.

00:47:00.734 --> 00:47:03.634
And you start ruining your health with that.

00:47:03.734 --> 00:47:09.467
It is a very, very surprising thing how people understand

00:47:09.534 --> 00:47:14.000
and like things which are very destructive.

00:47:14.067 --> 00:47:15.601
But you can manage.

00:47:15.701 --> 00:47:19.133
These are the modern times, where you can advertise,

00:47:19.234 --> 00:47:22.267
you can do all kinds of enticement, everything

00:47:22.367 --> 00:47:25.567
and you can manage this Mr. Ego very well,

00:47:25.667 --> 00:47:29.234
which pampers you. In this pampering,

00:47:29.300 --> 00:47:33.367
ego gets completely drowned and

00:47:33.467 --> 00:47:37.267
it loses its control over its own personality.

00:47:37.334 --> 00:47:40.634
Thus, many by people get lost into it.

00:47:40.701 --> 00:47:43.534
Now Christ has sacrificed His life

00:47:43.601 --> 00:47:45.801
and then He resurrected.

00:47:46.033 --> 00:47:48.367
In the same way, all such people

00:47:48.434 --> 00:47:52.367
who have ruined their lives have to come up

00:47:52.434 --> 00:47:56.667
through resurrection. there’s no other way out through Sahaja Yoga.

00:47:56.734 --> 00:48:02.100
When you understand your own value, you’ll understand everything.

00:48:02.167 --> 00:48:05.534
Otherwise, what is it? You are looking through your eyes

00:48:05.601 --> 00:48:07.501
or somebody else’s eyes?

00:48:07.567 --> 00:48:11.734
You are hearing through your ears or somebody else’s ear?

00:48:11.801 --> 00:48:16.400
It should be your own, so know thyself.

00:48:16.467 --> 00:48:20.767
When you know thyself, everything will work out very well.

00:48:21.000 --> 00:48:25.601
Out of this only, out of this category of people who know themselves

00:48:25.701 --> 00:48:28.100
Sahaja Yoga can be built up —

00:48:28.200 --> 00:48:32.267
not by people who do not know themselves.

00:48:32.334 --> 00:48:37.400
It’s a very, very long subject. I could go on on these two subjects,

00:48:37.467 --> 00:48:40.667
but the main thing is we have to be thankful

00:48:40.767 --> 00:48:46.334
to Christ for bringing this resurrection

00:48:46.400 --> 00:48:50.400
into play so that we get our discretion.

00:48:50.467 --> 00:48:52.767
Divine discretion, we’ll get it.

00:48:53.033 --> 00:48:58.200
It’s such a struggle, such a path He created,

00:48:58.300 --> 00:49:04.534
that we could go through this ordeal very easily,

00:49:04.601 --> 00:49:09.334
which will kill our ego and our conditionings.

00:49:10.334 --> 00:49:13.601
I am happy Sahaja Yogis will realise it

00:49:13.667 --> 00:49:16.467
and respect it within yourself,

00:49:16.567 --> 00:49:20.701
that you are seeing your ego and superego

00:49:20.801 --> 00:49:24.701
so clearly and that you could be above it.

00:49:24.767 --> 00:49:26.801
May God bless you all.